title: Warren Ellis  virtually complete bibliography - Planetary, Ultim
description:
it might be easier to say what I DON'T have here, but this torrent includes:

1992-3 Harlequin Bones
1993 Lazarus Churchyard + Sugarvirus
1994 Hellstorm + 2099 Unlimited
1995 Dr Strange, Druid, Excalibur, Marvel 2099, Pryde and Wisdom, Ruins,
	Starjammers, Thor, Ultraforce, What If
1996 DV8, Storm, X-Calibre, Legends of the Dark Knight
1997 Transmetropolitan, Wolverine, Vampirella, Gen 13
1998 assorted comics and non-fiction
1999 Bad Signal, Come in Alone, Hellblazer, Planetary, Strange Killings, The Authority
2000 City of Silence, Dark Blue, Counter X
2001: Bad World, Ministry Of Space, Superidol, The Operation 
2002 Global Frequency, Scars, Atmospherics, the Operation (Oni Color Special)
2003: Mek, Red, Reload, Tokyo Storm Warning, TwoStep, Orbiter, Switchblade Honey
2004 Apparat, Ocean, Ultimate FF
2005 Desolation Jones, Down, Fell, Iron Man, Jack Cross, JLA Classified, Ultimate Galactus Trilogy
2006 Black Gas, Nextwave, Wolfskin
2007 Black Summer, Doktor Sleepless, Newuniversal, Thunderbolts
2008 Anna Mercury, Freak Angels, No Hero, Ultimate Human, Astonishing X-Men
2009 Ignition City, Supergod, Ultimate Armor Wars, Frankensteins_Womb
2010 Captain Swing and the Electrical Pirates of Cindery Island, Astonishing X-Men Xenogenesis
2011 Secret Avengers Osborn #1 (backup story). Documentary: Captured Ghosts
2013 Avengers Endless Wartime Scatterlands. Fiction: Dead Pig Collector, Gun Machine. 

Bonus: Assorted other text-only pieces, Warren Ellis Biblio, Top 25 Warren Ellis Comics

Note: this includes issues Ellis wrote, so if you're looking for the complete run of the Authority or Hellstorm, that won't be here. I might post the complete run of the Authority separately, however.
